Sections.title: Welcome
Sections.content:
The Curriculum Vitae of Joe Buckle

I call myself a Full Stack Developer which means that I am comfortable working on all parts of the stack but I do not excel in any one area.

I have been doing this in a professional capacity for a little over 10 years but I have been an avid tinkerer much longer.
In this time I have developed experience in:

  • JavaScript
    • React + Redux
    • Express
    • Backbone
    • Angular
  • PHP
    • WordPress
    • Laravel
  • Python
    • Django
    • Wagtail
  • MySQL
  • Linux
  • ...many other things

Completely self-taught, self-motivated and forever learning.
